  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN YOUR OWN ANIMAL TRAINING CENTER!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animal Trainer Simulator gives you a unique opportunity to build, design, and run your own Training Center! Create the perfect space to make your pupils feel safe and happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOP YOUR TRAINING CENTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your training center with new attractions and amenities - jumping ramps, obstacle courses, slalom poles, tunnels and much more. Manage and expand the entire area, create a hall, add chairs, paint walls, build waiting rooms, and create a play area for animals. You have to remember that in your animal training center, there will be different species of animals - and therefore you have to think about the different spaces where they will stay. After all, each pet has its own unique needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TAKE CARE OF THEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exercise and training are not everything - your task in the game also will be to take care of the animals. Pet, brush, wash them and don't forget to give treats! Thanks to this, each pet will feel at home in your training center.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRAIN AND IMPROVE THE SKILLS OF THE ANIMALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of your main tasks in the game will be to train animals, teach them commands, and tricks. Much will depend on you and your approach to teaching animals, it requires a lot of work and commitment, but animals are able to repay with love and fidelity. Some of the animals will not be so eager to train and learn new habits, you have to find the right way to deal with them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARTICIPATE IN DIFFERENT COMPETITION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open a stud and a paddock, train them, and maybe one of your horses will win in the world championship! Hard training pays off, make your Training Center the best and known all over the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN YOUR OWN ANIMAL TRAINING CENTER!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animal Trainer Simulator gives you a unique opportunity to build, design, and run your own Training Center! Create the perfect space to make your pupils feel safe and happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOP YOUR TRAINING CENTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your training center with new attractions and amenities - jumping ramps, obstacle courses, slalom poles, tunnels and much more. Manage and expand the entire area, create a hall, add chairs, paint walls, build waiting rooms, and create a play area for animals. You have to remember that in your animal training center, there will be different species of animals - and therefore you have to think about the different spaces where they will stay. After all, each pet has its own unique needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.webm?